                Acasti Pharma, Inc. (ACST)  Full Company Report 










Company Summary














Acasti Pharma Inc. is a biopharmaceutical company. It is focused on research, development and commercialization of krill oil based forms of omega-3 phospholipid therapies. CaPre (R), Acasti's only prescription drug candidate, is being developed to help prevent and treat hypertriglyceridemia. ONEMIA (R) is a medical food and currently Acasti's only commercialized product. Acasti Pharma Inc. is headquartered in Laval, Canada.   




